    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Actual_Google_Launch_Date__c}" /> 
</apex:outputText>
Monthly Recurring Revenue:<apex:outputText value="{0, number, currency}">
    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Total_MRR__c}"/>
</apex:outputText> 
Last Month Media Budget: <apex:outputText value="{0, number, currency}">
    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Last_Month_Budget__c}"/>
</apex:outputText> 
Current Month Media Budget:<apex:outputText value="{0, number, currency}">
    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Current_Month_Budget__c}"/>
</apex:outputText> 
 
Client Paint Points:

Concerns or objections shared by Dealer: {!relatedTo.Concerns_or_objections_shared_by_Dealer__c}
How were the Dealer concerns addressed? {!relatedTo.How_were_concerns_addressed__c}
Dealer's response to addressed concerns? {!relatedTo.Client_s_feedback_to__c}

Account Performance:

High-Level Positive Account Performance: {!relatedTo.From_your_POV_what_has_been_going_well__c}
Areas for Improvement: {!relatedTo.Areas_for_Improvement__c}
Actions Needed to Save Account: {!relatedTo.Actions_Needed_to_Save_Account__c}

Next Steps: 

Any insight to date to consider? {!relatedTo.Any_insight_to_date_to_consider__c}
Save Call scheduled?  {!IF(relatedTo.Save_Call_Scheduled__c, 'Yes', 'No')}
Date of Save Call:  <apex:outputText value="{0, date,MM/dd/yyyy, h:mm a}">
                    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Date_of_Save_Call__c}" /> 
                </apex:outputText>
Beyond you and the AT, is there anyone else you’d like to include on the call? {!relatedTo.Anyone_else_you_d_like_to_include_on_Cal__c}  
Have you reached out to the Data team? {!IF(relatedTo.Have_you_reached_out_to_the_Data_team__c, 'Yes', 'No')}
Data’s deliverable date: <apex:outputText value="{0, date, MM/dd/yyyy}">
    <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Data_s_deliverable_date__c}" /> 
</apex:outputText>
